SubjectThunderchild First Nation Indian Reserve #115X, Saskatchewan ** Grant of Easement **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise by TRANSGAS LIMITED of the power to take an interest in lands within THUNDERCHILD FIRST NATION INDIAN RESERVE #115X in Saskatchewan; and (2) authorizing the Company, in lieu of such taking, the grant of the required easement.
